name: perm.client.DMSFile.r
condition: self.createdBy != ?  AND (self.metaFile.isShared = true OR self.metaFile.sharedWith = ? OR self.metaFile.sharedWith = ? OR self IN (SELECT d.parent FROM DMSFile d WHERE d.metaFile.isShared = true OR d.metaFile.sharedWith = ?  OR d.metaFile.sharedWith = ?))

name: perm.client.DMSFile.rcw
condition: self.createdBy = ? OR (self.metaFile.isShared = true OR self.metaFile.sharedWith = ? OR self.metaFile.sharedWith = ? OR self IN (SELECT d.parent FROM DMSFile d WHERE d.metaFile.isShared = true OR d.metaFile.sharedWith = ?  OR d.metaFile.sharedWith = ?))

name: perm.client.MetaFile.all
condition: self.createdBy = ? OR self.createdBy.partner = ? OR self.isShared = true OR self.sharedWith = ? OR self.sharedWith = ?

name: perm.base.Address.all
condition: self IN (SELECT pa.address FROM PartnerAddress pa WHERE pa.partner = ?)
